----------------
* How to build *
----------------
The git repo should be cloned into external/bluetooth under AOSP source tree.

At root of working AOSP Android build ennvironment, 
'make libbtctl' : for libbtctl

It is faster to build at local directory.
( cd external/bluetooth/libbtctl/libbtctl; mm)



------------------
* how to install *
------------------
On Android device running 4.3 or later,
adb root
adb remount
adb push out/target/product/panda/system/lib/libbtctl.so system/lib/libbtctl.so

